        repeatable = 'No',
        previous = {'More Questions Than Answers'},
        next = {'Chains and Bonds'},
        requirements = {
            {name = '[Key Item] CCB Polymer Pump', count = 1},
        },
        walkthrough = '1. Visit Cid at Metalworks (H-8) in Bastok for a cutscene.\n2. Travel to Sealion\'s Den via Tavnazia (near Home Point #2).\n3. Click the Iron Gate for a cutscene.\n4. Board the airship and click the door for another cutscene.\n5. Enter the "One to be Feared" battlefield (45-minute time limit).\n6. Defeat three sequential boss encounters:\n   Stage 1: Five Mammett-22 Zeta units.\n   - They change combat forms (H2H, Sword, Staff, Polearm).\n   - In H2H form they use Transmogrification (absorbs physical damage for ~30s).\n   - In Staff form they can be Silenced.\n   Stage 2: Omega.\n   - Uses predominantly AoE attacks with status effects.\n   - Fight steadily until ~25% HP, then use a CCB Polymer Pump to finish.\n   Stage 3: Ultima.\n   - Three-phase fight with varying abilities.\n   - Below ~20% HP it spams Antimatter. Use CCB Polymer Pump around 30% HP.\n7. HP/MP are restored between each stage on the airship deck.\n8. After completion, speak to Taillegeas in Ru\'Lude Gardens to unlock Trust: Cherukiki.',
        notes = 'The level cap for this fight has been lifted and it is now relatively trivial at higher levels. Bring CCB Polymer Pumps (purchasable from Goblins) to trivialise the Omega and Ultima fights.',
    },
