        title = '*Mist Melter (defeating Ouryu)',
        repeatable = nil,
        previous = {'Sheltering Doubt'},
        next = {'The Secrets of Worship'},
        requirements = nil,
        walkthrough = '1. Travel to the Dilapidated Gate at Misareaux Coast (F-7) for a cutscene.\n2. Navigate through Riverne - Site B01 toward Monarch Linn.\n   - Use Sneak and Invisible to bypass enemies.\n3. Obtain a Giant Scale by defeating wyverns in the area.\n4. Trade the Giant Scale to the Unstable Displacement at (G-8) to proceed.\n5. Progress through additional Spatial Displacements into Monarch Linn (uncapped).\n6. Enter "The Savage" battlefield and defeat Ouryu.\n   - Ouryu flies frequently — bring Mistmelts to force her to land.\n   - Key abilities: Absolute Terror, Horrid Roar (dispels buffs), Invincible phases.\n   - She has Stoneskin at the start — dispel if possible.\n   - The fight ends at around 30% HP.\n7. After the fight, speak with Justinius in Tavnazian Safehold (J-6, Map 1) to complete the mission.',
