        previous = {'The Savage'},
        next = {'Slanderous Utterings'},
        requirements = nil,
        walkthrough = '1. Silent Oil\n2. Reraise\n3. (Optional): Speak with Justinius at (J-6) on the top floor of the Tavnazian Safehold.\n   - If you receive the [Key Item] Monarch Linn Patrol Permit, this is for the Quest Uninvited Guests. Speak to Justinius again if this occurs.\n4. Examine the Walnut Door at (K-7) just up the ramp from Justinius for a cutscene.\n5. Travel to (G-4) in Misareaux Coast and check the Iron Gate for a cutscene and enter the Sacrarium.\n   - The Misareaux Coast Home Point #1 will bring you very close.\n6. Once inside, head to the maze section in the southeast of Sacrarium Map 1 to the right.\n   - The maze changes based on the game day, see the map for the current day\'s layout. Your goal is to move to connection point B, putting you on southwest section of Sacrarium Map 2.',
